      "note": "The Book: in a general sense, Revelation. \"Those to whom the Book hath been given\" are both (1) the People of the Book of previous revelations, who study the new Revelation in Arabic without prejudice and find in it confirmation of what their ancestors had received; and (2) the Muslims who receive the Qur'an with such spiritual joy."
